{"tid":651711,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個曼德拉效應","createTime":"2018-05-03T09:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T09:57:59.000Z","uid":154565,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"16ae8ee7e3c955ab63861831bd1401c193a627cf","tid":651711,"uid":154565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:49:59.000Z","msg":"曼德拉效應（英文：Mandela Effect），又叫虛假記憶（英文：False memory），係指有好多人都發覺記憶同事實有出入嘅現象。最早發現呢種現象係2010年一位研究超自然現象嘅美國人，佢發現自己同好多人一樣，印象入面南非總統曼德拉早喺1980年代已經喺監獄入面死咗，但現實係2010年嗰陣佢重在生（2013年先至死）。佢覺得咁多人同時記錯未必係巧合，可能涉及唔同嘅平行宇宙，不過而家未有科學方法證明到有無平行宇宙嘅存在。"},{"pid":"d1da4f585070b27c742cc976966e06089ca77952","tid":651711,"uid":154565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:51:07.000Z","msg":"我先：中國人並唔係東亞病夫 無左東亞"},{"pid":"532155771e036a648ebe1095f8908c72914e756c","tid":651711,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:52:35.000Z","msg":"你個topic已經係啦 明明係孟加拉效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4a9c4e5032a6f75965501a35dd5a858a27129e","tid":651711,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"532155771e036a648ebe1095f8908c72914e756c","tid":651711,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:52:35.000Z","msg":"你個topic已經係啦 明明係孟加拉效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4aa67c44a12af76bdc80ef9295590a817acc0b","tid":651711,"uid":129931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"532155771e036a648ebe1095f8908c72914e756c","tid":651711,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:52:35.000Z","msg":"你個topic已經係啦 明明係孟加拉效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:57:59.000Z","msg":"我印象都係孟加拉效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />